                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14345644" author="thobbs" created="Tue, 3 Mar 2015 20:06:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve updated the docs as commit  6ee0c757c3 and pushed the updated versions to the website.  Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14345711" author="jkrupan" created="Tue, 3 Mar 2015 20:49:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks. The change for the special variable names looks fine, but the grammar for LIMIT, TTL, and TIMESTAMP still says &quot;&amp;lt;integer&amp;gt;&quot; - it needs to be &quot;( &amp;lt;integer&amp;gt; | &amp;lt;variable&amp;gt; )&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
